#. VAR: īsakampoṇe → īsakapoṇe (bj, s1-3, km, pts1) | īsakaphaṇe (bj-a)
msgctxt "mn152:6.9"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, ānanda, īsakampoṇe padumapalāse udakaphusitāni pavattanti, na "
"saṇṭhanti;"
msgstr ""
"It’s like how a drop of water would roll off a gently sloping lotus leaf, "
"and would not stay there."

msgctxt "mn152:6.10"
msgid ""
"evameva kho, ānanda, yassa kassaci evaṃsīghaṃ evaṃtuvaṭaṃ evaṃappakasirena "
