"gandhesu."
msgstr ""
"In the training of the noble one this is called the supreme development of "
"the faculties regarding smells known by the nose."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya7"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "mn152:7.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, ānanda, bhikkhuno jivhāya rasaṃ sāyitvā uppajjati manāpaṃ, "
"uppajjati amanāpaṃ, uppajjati manāpāmanāpaṃ."
